We lost Willie Mays.

82
00:05:11,290 --> 00:05:12,720
- Mr. Broadbent.

83
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:13,820
- Dan.

84
00:05:13,820 --> 00:05:15,260
- Dan.

85
00:05:15,260 --> 00:05:16,510
You're breaking my heart.

86
