130
00:06:56,430 --> 00:06:58,980
- Oh, we're never gonna
get a cab at this hour.

131
00:06:58,980 --> 00:07:00,280
- We've got a car for you.

132
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,250
- Hello.
- Good morning.

133
00:07:09,254 --> 00:07:10,087
- Well.

134
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,961
We'll have to do this again sometime.

135
00:07:14,961 --> 00:07:16,294
- I'd like that.

136
00:07:17,710 --> 00:07:20,210
(light music)

137
00:07:21,930 --> 00:07:23,798
It was nice meeting you.

138
00:07:23,798 --> 00:07:24,670
- Bye.

139
00:07:24,670 --> 00:07:25,503
- [Tom] Bye.

