257
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,840
She'll be done at six.

258
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:04,160
If you can pick her up, don't call me.

259
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:05,793
- [Tom] Hi, it's Tom Cornell.

260
00:12:06,650 --> 00:12:09,320
